{"id":4805,"date":"2021-11-22T10:01:09","date_gmt":"2021-11-22T18:01:09","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/?p=4805"},"modified":"2021-11-22T10:02:34","modified_gmt":"2021-11-22T18:02:34","slug":"xr-super-series","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/xr-super-series\/","title":{"rendered":"XR Super Series"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4806\" src=\"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/XRSSlogo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"343\" height=\"147\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/XRSSlogo.jpg 343w, https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/XRSSlogo-300x129.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 343px) 100vw, 343px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>SFI is pleased to announce that the <a href=\"https:\/\/racexr.com\/xrss\/\">XR Super Series<\/a> has become a member sanctioning body. The XR Super Series is a 20-race sanctioned schedule of dirt racing events across the United States beginning in 2022.<\/p>\n<p>XR Events began an initiative in 2021 to produce and promote major dirt racing events for Super Late Models featuring class superstars and backed by high-paying purses &amp; enticing financial bonuses. In 2022, XR will take that effort a step further with a full slate of 20 race dates under the XR Super Series (XRSS) umbrella.<\/p>\n<p>The goal of the XRSS is to complement existing racing schedules with additional opportunities and to reward independent drivers and teams who choose to race these events. Also, starting in 2022, all 20 of these events will be officially sanctioned as XRSS races with a newly established rulebook and a full-time, in-house technical inspection team.<\/p>\n<p>The XR Super Series will feature stops at Bristol Motor Speedway (Tenn.), the Dirt Track at Charlotte Motor Speedway (N.C.), Belleville High Banks (Kan.), Stuart International Speedway (Iowa), the Texas Motor Speedway Dirt Track (Texas) and The Dirt Track at Las Vegas Motor Speedway (Nev.)<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>SFI is pleased to announce that the XR Super Series has become a member sanctioning body. The XR Super Series is a 20-race sanctioned schedule of dirt racing events across the United States beginning in 2022. XR Events began an initiative in 2021 to produce and promote<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[43,18,7,12,68],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4805","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-articles","category-autoracing","category-general","category-news","category-sanctioning-body"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4805","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4805"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4805\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4808,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4805\/revisions\/4808"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4805"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4805"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4805"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}